==English==

===Adjective===
'''sanguinary'''
# Accompanied by bloodshed. 
# Eager for bloodshed; bloodthirsty. 
# Consisting of blood. 

===Synonyms===
*[[bloodthirsty]]
*[[gory]]
*[[slaughterous]]
*[[butcherous]]

===Usage note===
Not to be confused with [[sanguine]].  ''Sanguine'' means 'optimistic', ''sanguinary'' means 'blood-thirsty, gory'.

